## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant literature in other languages. Additionally, the analysis relies on interpretations of existing literature, which may be subject to bias or varying interpretations. Further research could include empirical studies on the cognitive effects of literature to provide a more comprehensive understanding.